  <thing id="iUmDarKiss" name="Dark Kiss" description="{b}Alignment{/b} CE\n{b}Ego{/b} 13\n{b}Senses{/b} 30 ft. vision and hearing\n{b}Int{/b} 10, {b}Wis{/b} 12, {b}Cha{/b} 12 \n{b}Communication{/b} empathy \n{b}Lesser Power{/b}: {i}hold person{/i}on an enemy 3/day.\n\n{b}Personality{/b}: Dark Kiss, whose real name was forgotten, was a cold-blooded serial killer who killed for the sport of it. He was fond of decapitating his victims and stamping their foreheads with his sigil - the bloody impression of his lips. He called it his &quot;dark kiss&quot;. Eventually he was caught red-lipped, so to speak, and was lynched on the spot. The kukri he used in his killings, however, has continued to float throughout the land spawning numerous copycat killers over the years." compset="MagicWep" summary="{i}+3 vorpal ghost touch kukri{/i}" uniqueness="useronce">
