  <thing id="iUmMacBloo" name="Mace of Blood" description="This {i}+3 heavy mace{/i} must be coated in blood every day, or its bonus fades away (until the mace is coated again). The character using this mace must make a DC 13 Will save every day it is within his possession or become chaotic evil.\n\n{b}Note{/i}: The alignment change must be made manually\n\n{b}Construction{/b}\n{b}Requirements{/b}: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, creator must be at least 9th level and chaotic evil; {b}Cost{/b} 8,000 gp" compset="MagicWep" summary="{i}+3 heavy mace{/i}">
